1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper proposes an end-to-end framework that leverages the hierarchy of CNN for outfit compatibility prediction and diagnosis. 
2. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The proposed approach deals with fashion outfit images and their pairwise similarities, which falls under the domain of multimedia. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper introduces a learning-based approach for outfit compatibility prediction and diagnosis. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The fill-in-the-blank task mentioned in the paper can be seen as a form of information retrieval. 
5. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as fill-in-the-blank, which falls under the domain of computation and language.
